OL,3,CHospitals stand down critical incident
OL,4,Cafter pressures
OL,6,FA health trust has officially stood
OL,7,Fdown a critical incident which was
OL,8,Fdeclared after accident and emergency
OL,9,Fdepartments faced "exceptionally high
OL,10,Fdemand"
OL,12,FNHS University Hospitals of Liverpool
OL,13,FGroup brought in the measure on
OL,14,FTuesday, 7 January, due to sustained
OL,15,Fpressures at Aintree and Royal
OL,16,FLiverpool Hospital - with patients
OL,17,Freportedly waiting 50 hours for a bed
OL,18,Fon a ward.
