OL,3,CHospitals stand down critical incident
OL,4,Cafter pressures
OL,6,FHospital bosses said an influx of
OL,7,Fpatients suffering from winter viruses
OL,8,Fsuch as flu and norovirus were putting
OL,9,Fsevere pressure on the services they
OL,10,Fprovide.
OL,12,FIn an update on Monday, 13 January,
OL,13,Fthe Trust stood down the critical
OL,14,Fincident and said they are "working
OL,15,Fhard" to treat people quickly.
