OL,3,CHospitals stand down critical incident
OL,4,Cafter pressures
OL,6,FIt has urging anyone who needs to
OL,7,Fattend the accident and emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment, or the hospital for an
OL,9,Fappointment, to follow infection
OL,10,Fcontrol measures to "help curb the
OL,11,Fspread of viruses".
OL,13,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for NHS
OL,14,FUniversity Hospitals of Liverpool
OL,15,FGroup said: "We would like to thank
OL,16,Fmembers of the public who have
OL,17,Fsupported us by choosing other
OL,18,Fservices, such as a GP, local pharmacy
OL,19,For walk-in centre, as it means we have
OL,20,Fbeen able to focus our efforts on our
OL,21,Fsickest patients.
