OL,3,CHospitals stand down critical incident
OL,4,Cafter pressures
OL,6,F"Colleagues at Aintree and Royal
OL,7,FLiverpool hospitals have been working
OL,8,Fhard to see and treat people as
OL,9,Fquickly as possible and, where
OL,10,Fappropriate, get them home to their
OL,11,Floved ones.
OL,13,F"We know that there are high levels of
OL,14,Fflu, respiratory illness and winter
OL,15,Fbugs in the community, which has
OL,16,Fimpacted our Emergency Departments.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
