OL,3,CHospitals stand down critical incident
OL,4,Cafter pressures
OL,6,F"If you are attending our EDs,
OL,7,Fpatients and visitors should follow
OL,8,Fsome additional infection control
OL,9,Fmeasures to help curb the spread of
OL,10,Fwinter viruses such as flu and
OL,11,Fnorovirus.
OL,13,F"This includes practicing good hand
OL,14,Fhygiene, only visiting the areas they
OL,15,Fneed to in our hospitals and wearing
OL,16,Fmasks in clinical areas if asked to do
OL,17,Fso."
OL,19,FA critical incident remains in place
OL,20,Ffor Whiston Hospital in Knowsley and
OL,21,FArrowe Park Hospital on the Wirral.
